---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Contact - Neon Injector"
  description="Get in touch with the Neon Injector team for support, feedback, or inquiries about our Mobile Legends skin customization tool."
>
  <div class="flex flex-col min-h-screen">
    <main class="flex-1 pt-16">
      <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 text-[var(--text-color)]">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-neon-purple mb-8 text-center">Contact Us</h1>
        <div class="prose max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
          <p class="mb-6">The Neon Injector team is dedicated to ensuring you have the best experience with our tool. Whether you need help with setup, have questions about skin customization, want to report a bug, or wish to share feedback, weâ€™re here to assist you promptly and professionally.</p>
          
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-8">How to Reach Us</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">You can contact us through multiple channels for your convenience. We aim to respond to all inquiries within 24-48 hours, though response times may vary depending on the volume of requests. Choose the method that works best for you:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-3 mb-6">
            <li><strong>Contact Form</strong>: Use the form below to send us a detailed message directly from this page.</li>
            <li><strong>Email</strong>: Reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a> for direct communication.</li>
            <li><strong>Discord Community</strong>: Join our <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Discord server</a> to connect with our team and other users, share tips, and get real-time support.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          <div class="bg-[var(--card-bg)] p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg border border-neon-purple-dark">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Send Us a Message</h2>
            <p class="mb-6 text-sm">Please provide your name, email, and a detailed message so we can assist you effectively. All fields are required to ensure we can follow up with you.</p>
            <form action="/submit-contact" method="POST" class="space-y-4">
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="block text-sm font-medium">Your Name</label>
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="name"
                  name="name"
                  class="w-full p-2 rounded bg-[var(--input-bg)] text-[var(--text-color)] border border-neon-purple-dark focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neon-purple"
                  required
                  placeholder="Enter your name"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block text-sm font-medium">Your Email</label>
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  name="email"
                  class="w-full p-2 rounded bg-[var(--input-bg)] text-[var(--text-color)] border border-neon-purple-dark focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neon-purple"
                  required
                  placeholder="Enter your email address"
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label for="message" class="block text-sm font-medium">Your Message</label>
                <textarea
                  id="message"
                  name="message"
                  rows="5"
                  class="w-full p-2 rounded bg-[var(--input-bg)] text-[var(--text-color)] border border-neon-purple-dark focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-neon-purple"
                  required
                  placeholder="Describe your question or issue"
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              <button
                type="submit"
                class="bg-neon-purple hover:bg-neon-purple-light text-white font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition duration-300"
              >
                Submit Message
              </button>
            </form>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8 text-center">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-4">Alternative Contact Methods</h3>
            <p class="mb-3">Email: <a href="mailto:support@neon-injector.my.id" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">support@neon-injector.my.id</a></p>
            <p class="mb-3">Discord: <a href="https://discord.gg/neoninjector" class="text-neon-purple hover:text-neon-purple-light">Join our Discord server</a></p>
            <p class="text-sm italic">Response Time: We aim to respond within 24-48 hours, depending on inquiry volume.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </div>
</Layout>